-- Yamana Gold to Buy Extorre For About $414 Million in Cash, Stock
-- B y   J e s s i c a   R e s n i c k - A u l t
-- 2012-06-18T11:09:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-18/yamana-gold-to-buy-extorre-for-about-414-million-in-cash-stock.html
Yamana Gold Inc. (YRI)  agreed to buy
 Extorre Gold Mines Ltd. (XG)  for about C$414 ($404.1) million in cash
and shares.  Extorre shareholders will receive C$3.50 in cash and 0.0467
percent of a share of Yamana, according to a statement from
Extorre today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jessica Resnick-Ault at 
 jresnickault@bloomberg.net  